review_blob:
Nice hazy straw color,  aroma is sweet Belgian blonde,  taste is sweet Belgian with noticeable hops
Drinkable but not my favorite.  Wouldnt turn one down but wont buy anymore.

I think very similar to New Holland Dragons Milk.  Delicious,  oaky bourbon barrels, smoke, sweet caramel, vanilla and roasted malts. A bit of earthy.   Pour a snifter, sit back and enjoy.  Great beer.
